Klasse FlightData

java.lang.Object
app.data.FlightData
public class FlightData extends Object
FlightData holds all in-memory flight-related data for drones. Provides functions to extract specific analytics.

    • getDynamicsByType

      public Map<String, List<DroneDynamics>> getDynamicsByType(String type)
      Get all DroneDynamics-Data of every Drone that corresponds to the given DroneType.
      Parameter:
      type - Drohnen-Typ-Code (example SkSk..., HoHs..., etc.)
      Gibt zurück:
      Map with Key = Drone-Label (example "Eachine: E58 : AAA2-440.0"), Value = List of all Dynamics of the given DroneType.
